short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Puts MrGreen from LCOLONQ on every YouTube thumbnail.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
MrGreen from LCOLONQ in various versions (and maybe some imposters) will be displayed on every YouTube thumbnail.

You can enable and disable the extension by clicking on its icon.
